snippet.title: Garden of the Sea Announcement Trailer - Oculus Quest 2
snippet.description:
Garden of the Sea will leave early access and release in 1.0 January 13th 2022!

You wake up on a small island in a magical world. Grow your garden, nurture local creatures, furnish your home or adventure across the seas to explore more islands and gather new resources. This world is for you.

Get the game here:

Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1086850/Garden_of_the_Sea/
Oculus: https://www.oculus.com/experiences/quest/3684804704932159

Official plushie: https://shop.makeship.com/3rwUHuR

Follow https://twitter.com/NeatCorp and https://twitter.com/GotS_VR on twitter for more updates!
Also join our discord at https://discord.com/invite/neatcorp

#GardenoftheSea #VR #NeatCorp
